            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                
                <h1>Third-party sign-in</h1>
                <p>CEF third-party sign-in service provides unified SDK to help developers implement WeChat, QQ and Weibo Sign-in, shortens development time for developers and helps APP to quickly get users. User data from various platforms will be centrally stored in the CEF background for greater convenience in access and analysis.</p>
                <br/>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/service/customer-engagement-fabric-8.png" alt=""/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <p>Implements personalized product Sign-in. Members will no longer be required to memorize passwords and they will skip to commonly used third-party sign-in.</p>
                        <p>Third-party sign-in service simplifies the registration process and helps APP quickly get users.</p>
                        <p>Convenience for developers to get user information and implement user portrait to provide a personalized user experience.</p>
